sql:
SELECT SUM(stock_quantity) AS total_in_stock
FROM inventory
WHERE region_id = (SELECT region_id FROM regions WHERE region_name = 'EU');

external_knowledge:
John Doe refers to the customer with the email 'john.doe@example.com'; 
Inventory details include inventory IDs, product IDs, size IDs, region IDs, stock quantities, last update dates, inventory statuses, reorder levels, reorder quantities, and conversion values; 
Preferred products and regions refer to the products and regions specified in the customer's preferences.
